Install
-------
Using  Python 3.8, 3.9, or 3.10.

Install the latest version of HONyx:

    $ pip install honyx

Required dependancies include [NetworkX](https://networkx.org/), [Numpy](https://numpy.org/) and [Scipy](https://scipy.org/).

